SELECT INTERMEDIA.SCLIENT, CLIENT.SCLIENAME, BRANPROD_ALLOW.NBRANCH FROM INTERMEDIA INTERMEDIA JOIN CLIENT CLIENT ON CLIENT.SCLIENT = INTERMEDIA.SCLIENT JOIN BRANPROD_ALLOW BRANPROD_ALLOW ON BRANPROD_ALLOW.NINTERMED = INTERMEDIA.NINTERMED WHERE BRANPROD_ALLOW.NBRANCH = 2 AND INTERMEDIA.NINT_STATUS = 1 AND ( INTERMEDIA.NINTERTYP = 4 OR INTERMEDIA.NINTERTYP = 91 OR INTERMEDIA.NINTERTYP = 92 OR INTERMEDIA.NINTERTYP = 93 OR INTERMEDIA.NINTERTYP = 95 )
